Intro Linux
========

# chapter 4

1. $ who -r
check the current run level

2. $ info grub
find the description of grub

3. $ xterm

4. $ jobs
show all the jobs

5. $ at 

6. $ cron

7. $ ps auxw | grep bash
show all process with name of bash

8. $ uptime

9. $  sudo du -sh *
disk utility show the disk usage

